\par }{\i\fs24 Restricted textures:  }{\fs24 All textures in the \ldblquote 
dmonly" subdir are for use in dm levels only.  They are human made brick type textures and are not appropriate to this pak.  Please do not use these textures in regular single player levels without prior permission.  If you have these textures in your 
\ldblquote bricks\rdblquote  subdirectory, please remove them.
\par }{\b\fs24 
